      <title>澳大利亚斥资6亿澳元监管网络​​色情，保护家庭暴力受害者</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-police-internet-porn-spend-600-mln-domestic-violence-victims-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚将花费近10亿澳元为那些逃离家庭暴力的人提供救助，并推出新措施来打击互联网上的色情和暴力行为，以应对政府所称的性别暴力“国家危机”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-police-internet-porn-spend-600-mln-domestic-violence-victims-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 03:16:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国国王批准前外交官马里斯担任外交部长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-king-approves-ex-diplomat-maris-foreign-minister-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官方《皇家公报》周三称，退休外交官马里斯·桑吉安蓬萨 (Maris Sangianmpongsa) 已被泰国国王认可为该国新任外交部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-king-approves-ex-diplomat-maris-foreign-minister-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:59:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾称中国海警加剧南海紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-chinese-coast-guard-elevating-tensions-south-china-sea-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名官员称，菲律宾周三指责中国海岸警卫队使用水炮袭击两艘菲律宾船只，加剧了南海紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-chinese-coast-guard-elevating-tensions-south-china-sea-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:40:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾对中国就职后的演习保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-post-inauguration-chinese-drills-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾最高安全官员周三表示，在当选总统赖清德本月就职后，台湾对中国进行军事演习保持警惕，并指出北京通常在六月开始此类演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-post-inauguration-chinese-drills-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于芯片需求增长，韩国出口连续第七个月增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-exports-rise-seventh-month-growing-chip-demand-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三贸易数据显示，韩国 4 月份出口连续第七个月增长，因对芯片的强劲需求继续引领增长，同时汽车销量和美国出货量攀升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-exports-rise-seventh-month-growing-chip-demand-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 00:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚澳洲航空正在调查忠诚度应用程序数据泄露的报告</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/australias-qantas-probing-reports-data-breach-frequent-flyers-app-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚航空公司周三表示，在媒体报道称存在允许用户访问其他乘客旅行信息的数据泄露事件后，该公司正在调查影响其飞行常客申请的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/australias-qantas-probing-reports-data-breach-frequent-flyers-app-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 00:48:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>成本上升及抵押贷款竞争导致澳大利亚银行利润缩水</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/australia-banks-face-profit-squeeze-rising-costs-mortgage-competition-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚最大的银行可能会报告上半年利润疲弱，因为高运营成本以及销售抵押贷款和存款的竞争挤压了利润率，分析师称股市上涨导致该行业过热，这可能会出现逆转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/australia-banks-face-profit-squeeze-rising-costs-mortgage-competition-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 00:46:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚零售商 Woolworths 将出售 Endeavour Group 价值 3.03 亿美元的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australian-retailer-woolworths-sell-303-mln-stake-endeavour-group-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚零售商 Woolworths 周三表示，将出售 Endeavor Group 5% 的股份，价值 4.68 亿澳元（约合 3.0284 亿美元），距离将这家酒类商店和酒吧运营商分拆近三年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australian-retailer-woolworths-sell-303-mln-stake-endeavour-group-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:23:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>极端高温导致学校关闭，全球学习差距扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/extreme-heat-is-closing-schools-widening-learning-gaps-worldwide-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[达卡九年级学生 Hena Khan 本周由于首都气温超过 40 摄氏度（104 华氏度），她很难集中精力学习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/extreme-heat-is-closing-schools-widening-learning-gaps-worldwide-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:08:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国劳工官员呼吁企业退出中国新疆</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/us-labor-official-calls-companies-exit-chinas-xinjiang-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国劳工部官员周二表示，出于对强迫劳动的担忧，国际公司无法在新疆负责任地运营，应该离开中国西部地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/us-labor-official-calls-companies-exit-chinas-xinjiang-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:46:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
